uschrist.org/study/scriptures/nt/eph/6.1-4?lang=eng","category":"Marriage & Family","subcategory":""},{"author":"Faust","reference":"","text":"“Noble fatherhood gives us a glimpse of the divine”","link":"","category":"Marriage & Family","subcategory":""},{"author":"Quorum of the Twelve","reference":"1973","text":"“It is significant that of all the titles of respect and honor and admiration that are given to Deity, He asked us to address Him as Father”","link":"","category":"Marriage & Family","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"Mosiah 10:12-17","text":"Lamanite-Nephite backstory","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/10.12-17?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"Alma 45:18-19","text":"Curious end of Alma; disappeared, thought to be taken by Spirit","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.18-19?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"Alma 47","text":"Amalickiah, wanted to be king of Nephites, cast out by Moroni, became king of Lamanites after crazy twist","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/47?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"Alma 54","text":"Ammoron and Moroni text each other with rage","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/54?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"Helaman 5:43-48","text":"Nice ministry of angels scene","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.43-48?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"3 Nephi 28:17-23","text":"The three Nephites","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.17-23?lang=eng","category":"Storyline","subcategory":""},{"author":"","reference":"4 Nephi 1","text":"All become good, all become evil","link":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/s